Show the status of ADE tasks.

Check .ade/tasks/ for active tasks and report:
- Task ID, description, current phase (0-10)
- Phase name: Intent → Research → Plan → Design Check → Implement →
  Quality Gate → Review → Verify → Documentation → Commit & PR → Retrospective
- Iteration counts (design check, code review, QA fix, verify reject)
- Active worktrees (git worktree list)
- Last progress log entries
